Uses of Package
de.wwu.muggl.configuration

Packages that use de.wwu.muggl.configuration
de.wwu.muggl.configuration Provides Classes for the constant and variable configuration of this application and the possibility to save them. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions Provides the packages for the instructions representing the bytecode instructions as well as abstract classes and interfaces for them. 
de.wwu.muggl.symbolic.flow.defUseChains Provides classes for data flow coverage measurement. 
de.wwu.muggl.symbolic.searchAlgorithms.choice Provides general classes for choice points. 
de.wwu.muggl.symbolic.searchAlgorithms.support Provides supportive functionality for the search algorithms implementations. 
de.wwu.muggl.symbolic.testCases Provides functionality needed to generate test cases from the information gained by the symbolic execution. 
de.wwu.muggl.ui.gui Provides the application's graphical user interface including supportive components. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.classfile Provides the representation of a classfile along with packages that contain the classfile structure's representations. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.classfile.structures.attributes Provides the representations for structures used by attributes of a classfile. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.exceptions Provides the Exception handler used by the virtual machine alone with the VmRuntimeException class which represents runtime exceptions in this virtual machine implementation. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.execution Provides algorithms needed during the execution and other execution related classes. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.impl.symbolic Provides the symbolic virtual machine implementation. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.initialization Provides initialization classes.
